course_title: The Personal and Social Development of the Adult

63A.comments: This is a core course for a Minor in Education, Interpersonal Development and for the Diploma in Education - Guidance Studies.This is an elective course for the Certificate in Health  and  Wellness.Registration is restricted to students in the Faculty of Education for the first three weeks of registration.The registration restrictions will be removed July 30, 2020.Registration will be blocked when all the seats are filled.A waitlist is available for this course - CNPS 433 W3A.
